question: Seeking an american restaurant, ideally within 180 kilometers of Gopher State Railroad Museum, MN. Can you find me its location?
sql:
SELECT * FROM pois
WHERE ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.582632 44.583053)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND amenity = 'restaurant'
AND cuisine ILIKE '%american%';

answers.description: Funky alley & bar hosts DJs plus music & theater performers while serving a simple American menu.
Late-night 2-story fixture offers American cuisine, drinks & live music in an industrial-chic space.
